    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved their required levels under MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. This model has been applied in clinical research supporting pre-submission interactions with FDA. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated decision-making purpose.",
